## 🤖 The AI Assistant Modes — Product Design

### Mode 1: "Ask PayWise" — The Conversational Assistant

**What it does:** Users type natural language queries, get instant financial intelligence.

**Example Conversations:**
```
User: "I'm ordering from Swiggy, ₹800. Best way to pay?"
PayWise: "Use PhonePe with your HDFC Millennia card:
  • PhonePe cashback: ₹40 (5%)
  • HDFC bank offer: ₹100 flat (on ₹500+)
  • Use code SWIGGY50 for ₹50 off
  Total savings: ₹190 on an ₹800 order! 🎉
  
  [Open PhonePe] [Copy Promo Code]"
```

```
User: "How much did I spend on food delivery this month?"
PayWise: "Your food delivery spending in February:
  • Total: ₹4,850 (across 12 orders)
  • Swiggy: ₹3,200 (8 orders)
  • Zomato: ₹1,650 (4 orders)
  • You saved ₹580 using PayWise recommendations
  
  💡 Tip: If you switch your Thursday orders to PhonePe,
  you could save an extra ₹200/month."
```

**Technical Implementation:**
- **LLM:** Google Gemini 2.0 Flash (free tier: 15 RPM, 1M TPM — enough for MVP)
- **RAG Pipeline:** Embed offer data + user transaction history into context
- **Function Calling:** LLM calls our existing APIs (`/api/recommend`, `/api/savings/stats`)
- **Guardrails:** Never expose raw financial data; always summarize; block prompt injection

### Mode 2: "Smart Savings" — Proactive Intelligence

**What it does:** Analyzes your spending patterns and proactively suggests savings.

**Features:**
1. **Weekly Savings Report** — "You could have saved ₹340 this week. Here's how."
2. **Smart Alerts** — "Your Jio recharge is due tomorrow. Use Amazon Pay to save ₹30."
3. **Category Budgets** — "You've spent 80% of your food delivery budget with 10 days left."
4. **Bill Optimizer** — "Switch your Netflix payment from SBI to HDFC → save ₹180/year."
5. **Price Drop Alerts** — "PhonePe increased Swiggy cashback from 5% to 10% today!"

### Mode 3: "Finance Dashboard" — Personal Finance Overview

**What it does:** One-screen view of your financial health related to digital payments.

**Sections:**
- 💰 **Total Saved All Time** with monthly trend chart
- 📊 **Spending by Category** (Food, Shopping, Bills, Travel)
- 🏦 **Payment Method Usage** (which apps you use most)
- 🔥 **Active Offers for You** (personalized, not generic)
- 📈 **Savings Streak** (gamification)
- 🎯 **Monthly Savings Goal** progress bar

