## ⚠️ Honest Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|
| **LLM hallucination** (wrong financial advice) | 🔴 High | Strict guardrails + always show source offer + disclaimer |
| **User doesn't log transactions** (cold start) | 🟡 Medium | Start with offer recommendations (no data needed), add transaction tracking gradually |
| **AI API costs at scale** | 🟡 Medium | Use Gemini Flash (free tier), cache common queries, batch processing |
| **Competition copies features** | 🟡 Medium | Speed of execution + community data moat + AI personalization |
| **Data breach** | 🔴 High | E2E encryption, RLS, audit logs, no payment data stored |
| **Supabase limitations at scale** | 🟢 Low | Migrate to managed PostgreSQL when hitting limits |

